dc_title_s: Geologic atlas of Todd County, Minnesota, C-18, Part A, Plate 5, Depth to Bedrock, Bedrock Topography, and Sand Distribution Model
dc_description_s: Maps showing the elevation of the bedrock surface (bedrock topography) and thickness of unconsolidated material over the bedrock surface and digitally created 3-dimensional surfaces and thickness of glacial and stream derived sand bodies, scale 1:200,000; 1:350,000, Todd County.
